<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-GLhlTQ8iRABdZLl6O3oVMWSktQOp6b7In1Zl3/Jr59b6EGGoI1aFkw7cmDA6j6gD"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <title>Url Shortener</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="m-4 text-center">URL SHORTENER</h1>
      <p class="text-center text-info">
        Welcome to our URL shortening service! We know that long URLs can be a
        hassle to share, especially on platforms like Twitter where character
        limits are strict. That's where our website comes in. With our service,
        you can easily and quickly shorten any URL, making it easier to share
        with friends, family, and colleagues.So why
        wait? Start shortening your links today and experience the convenience
        of our URL shortening service!
      </p>
      <form action="/shortUrl" method="post" class="d-flex">
        <input
          type="text"
          class="form-control"
          required
          placeholder="url"
          name="fullUrl"
          id="fullUrl
        "
        />
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success px-4 p-2 mx-2">
          Shrink
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-w76AqPfDkMBDXo30jS1Sgez6pr3x5MlQ1ZAGC+nuZB+EYdgRZgiwxhTBTkF7CXvN"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
